\[V \leq \mathcal{O}\left(\frac{\eta^{2}}{\rho}\right)+\frac{\eta\rho}{2\lambda }\cdot\mathbb{E}[\|\nabla f(x_{t})\|^{2}]+\mathcal{O}\left(\eta\right)\cdot\frac {1}{M}\sum_{m=1}^{M}\mathbb{E}[\|x_{t}^{m}-x_{t}\|^{2}]+\mathcal{O}\left(\eta^ {2}\right)\] \[IV \leq \mathcal{O}\left(\eta^{2}\right)\] \[III \leq \mathcal{O}\left(\eta\right)\cdot\frac{1}{M}\sum_{m=1}^{M} \mathbb{E}[\|\Gamma_{t-1}^{m}-\Gamma_{t}^{m}\|]\] \[II \leq \mathcal{O}\left(\eta\right)\cdot\frac{1}{M}\sum_{m=1}^{M} \mathbb{E}[\|g_{t}-\widetilde{g}_{t}^{m}\|]\] \[I \leq -\frac{\eta}{2C_{0}}\mathbb{E}\|\nabla f(x_{t})\|^{2}+\mathcal{O} \left(\eta\right)\cdot\frac{1}{M}\sum_{m=1}^{M}\mathbb{E}\left[\|x_{t}-x_{t}^ {m}\|^{2}\right]+\mathcal{O}\left(\eta\right)\cdot\frac{1}{M}\sum_{m=1}^{M} \mathbb{E}[\|\Gamma_{t-1}^{m}-\Gamma_{t}^{m}\|]\]

